text: Jaroslav Kopřiva (born 23 October 1990) is a Czech bobsledder. He competed in the four-man event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of the Czech Republic Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
